<p class="ql-align-center">一带一路首席国际童模达赛形象大使——郝泽铮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=211820835&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
